PrecisAmendments to the INDIAN BANDS REVENUE MONEYS REGULATIONS which add three Indian Bands to the schedule of bands authorized to control, administer and expend its revenue moneys. 1. Cold Lake Band of Indians (Alberta) 2. Broman Lake Band of Indians (B.C.) 3. Matsqui Band of Indians (B.C.)
